      "heading": "Drag and Drop Configuration for Symbols",
      "level": 2,
      "content": {
        "paragraphs": [
          "Here you can specify which control should be displayed when you drag and drop a symbol directly from the Symbol Explorer to a panel. You can select different controls for the various symbol types.",
          "Only the permissible controls are displayed for each symbol type.",
          "Binary",
          "Byte Array",
          "Floating Point",
          "Integer",
